OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,FThe boyfriend of a woman who was
OL,7,Funlawfully killed by her father during
OL,8,Fa visit to his home in Texas has
OL,9,Flabelled the police response as
OL,10,F"dismissive" and "upsetting".
OL,12,FLucy Harrison had been staying with
OL,13,Fher dad Kris Harrison and his family
OL,14,Fin Prosper, Texas, when shortly before
OL,15,F3pm on 10 January 2025, she was shot
OL,16,Fin the chest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
