OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,FThe 23-year-old fashion buyer from
OL,7,FWarrington, Cheshire, had travelled
OL,8,Fthere with her boyfriend Sam Littler
OL,9,Ffor a holiday after her dad moved when
OL,10,Fshe was a child, Cheshire Coroner's
OL,11,FCourt was told.
OL,13,FWhile no criminal charges were brought
OL,14,Fagainst Harrison, an inquest into
OL,15,FLucy's death in February 2026 found
OL,16,Fshe was unlawfully killed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,FIn a statement, her boyfriend Sam said
OL,7,Fhe had "taken time to process the
OL,8,Fevidence heard" and wanted to add his
OL,9,Fown account of the hours following her
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,FHe said: "Hearing the evidence in full
OL,13,Fwas devastating, but it confirmed many
OL,14,Fof the concerns I had carried
OL,15,Fprivately since Lucy's death.
OL,17,F"The coroner found that Kris had been
OL,18,Fdrinking continuously on 10 January
OL,19,F2025 and had also admitted to drinking
OL,20,Fthe day before, without the knowledge
OL,21,Fof anyone else in the household."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,FHe went on to explain that he was in
OL,7,Fshock immediately after the shooting,
OL,8,Fbut still remembers feeling "confused"
OL,9,Fby Harrison's behaviour.
OL,11,FHe said: "His demeanour, as seen in
OL,12,Fthe bodycam footage shown during the
OL,13,Finquest, has remained difficult for me
OL,14,Fto understand and process.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,F"The footage also captured a moment
OL,7,Fwhere someone said, "They were due to
OL,8,Fgo back today," to which the response
OL,9,Fheard was, 'Well they're not now.'
OL,10,FThat exchange remains one of the most
OL,11,Fpainful parts of the footage for me to
OL,12,Frevisit."
OL,14,FSam went on to criticise the Texas
OL,15,Fpolice's response, claiming he raised
OL,16,Fconcerns over Harrison's drinking to
OL,17,Finvestigators during his interview.
OL,26,@oD@UOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,FHe said: "Despite officers being aware
OL,7,Fthat alcohol had been consumed, and
OL,8,Fdespite Kris being the only other
OL,9,Fperson in the room when Lucy was shot,
OL,10,Fno breathalyser or blood alcohol test
OL,11,Fwas carried out.
OL,13,F"Given the seriousness of the
OL,14,Fincident, I struggled to understand
OL,15,Fwhy objective testing was not
OL,16,Fundertaken at the time."
OL,18,FHe said he was interviewed just
OL,19,Fmoments after learning Lucy had died,
OL,20,Fand was later questioned on why he did
OL,21,Fnot raise certain issues.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,FHe said: "I explained that I had been
OL,7,Finterviewed only minutes after being
OL,8,Finformed that Lucy had died and had
OL,9,Fnot been contacted again afterwards to
OL,10,Fclarify or expand upon my account. I
OL,11,Freturned to the UK the following day
OL,12,Fand was not contacted further by US
OL,13,Fauthorities in the weeks that
OL,14,Ffollowed."
OL,16,FSam finished his statement by
OL,17,Fquestioning whether the Texas Grand
OL,18,FJury was aware of all of the facts
OL,19,Fbefore they decided not to pursue
OL,20,Fcharges against Harrison.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,FIn Texas, a jury comprised of 12
OL,7,Fpeople are asked to determine whether
OL,8,Fthere is probable cause for certain
OL,9,Ffelonies before an individual is
OL,10,Fcharged.
OL,12,FSam said: "I do not know whether the
OL,13,FGrand Jury was provided with evidence
OL,14,Frelating to alcohol consumption that,
OL,15,Faccording to the coroner's findings,
OL,16,Fwas unknown to others in the
OL,17,Fhousehold... or the post-mortem
OL,18,Ffindings regarding the downward
OL,19,Ftrajectory of the bullet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,F"I also do not know whether they were
OL,7,Fshown the bedroom diagram included
OL,8,Fwithin the UK inquest bundle, which
OL,9,Frecorded the location of the bullet
OL,10,Fcasing near the bedside table, the
OL,11,Flocation of the firearm near the
OL,12,Fopposite lower corner of the bed and
OL,13,Fblood staining near the entrance to
OL,14,Fthe en-suite bathroom.
OL,16,F"I personally struggled to reconcile
OL,17,Fthe physical evidence shown in that
OL,18,Fdiagram with the account that Lucy had
OL,19,Fbeen standing beside Kris when the gun
OL,20,Fwas removed from its case.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1779315076
OL,3,CBoyfriend of woman 'unlawfully killed'
OL,4,Cby dad in US criticises Police response
OL,6,F"I do not know whether the Grand Jury
OL,7,Fwas informed that the firearm was
OL,8,Ffound to be in full working order, or
OL,9,Fthat the bullet itself was never
OL,10,Frecovered."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
